INSTALLATION

    % git clone <repository> example-myapp && cd example-myapp
    % cinnamon development deploy:setup
    % cinnamon development carton:install
    % cinnamon development server:start


Then access to:

    http://<hostname>:8080/

UPDATE

    % cinnamon development deploy:update
    % cinnamon development carton:install
    % cinnamon development server:restart

PRE_REQUIREMENTS

    * Cinnamon
    * Config::Pit

SEE ALSO

    http://blog.kentarok.org/entry/2012/02/23/015712
